Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:33.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:35.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  你還穿的是夏裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你已經換冬裝了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.37,Takagi san—Picture 04-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270.6\pos(1662,486)}換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:50.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為天氣預報說今天會降溫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原來西片你還會看天氣預報呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在賭我倆會不會在同一天換裝  會的話算我贏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:02.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,自作主張比起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好吧  就算西片你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  這感覺勝之不武啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  自己挑起比賽又自己認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是蠢到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且天氣冷了還穿夏裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不怎麼怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,別逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  如果高木同學說冷的話就算我贏如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我承認冷也能算你贏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總之  比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:42.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:51.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然有些岔開話題  關於漢字的歷史…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:54.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我爸爸又說他看到UFO了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,回去以後一定要給家長看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:13.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我故意今天一整天沒有做出讓她說冷的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:18.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她一定覺得我已經把比賽的事情給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然有點唐突  我給你出個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本跑得比鮑勃快  但比薩姆慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這三個人賽跑的話  誰是最後一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:34.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:35.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼薩姆是第幾名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  連起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,薩姆第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.00,Takagi san—Picture 04-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1320,648)\clip(1208,282.667,1456,322.667)\t(0,1000,\clip(1208,296,1442.667,698.667))}Sam \N\Nichi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,薩姆一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1280,672)}Samui \N\Nchi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,冷地！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果西片說喊疼  就是你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼說來著  不是按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:58.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,Seitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:58.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,推拿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,itai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,背疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要把上次被捉弄的份加倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來吧高木同學  回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想  薩姆是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你想讓我說冷字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學以前不是故作從容說過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,和天氣預報一樣  降溫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學好像不會對我說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那她只能同意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我說「嗯」   你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片會幫我取暖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,會幫我取暖的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這個…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,輸了  輸了  我認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片一遇到這種情況就沒轍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:50.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,既然我贏了  作為懲罰遊戲罰你幫我取暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:08.76,Takagi san—Picture 04-3,,0,0,0,,{\frz271.1\pos(506,414)}冬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:15.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以說  為什麼明明說好了要一起換裝  卻成這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,美奈  你沒給早苗發消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,發過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(792,364)}好——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,568)}再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,750)}明天開始穿冬裝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.65,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,404)}{\fs90}明天開始穿冬裝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1062,886)}{\fs30}發送失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.65,Takagi san—Picture 04-4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,810)}{\fs55}發送失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這條消息沒發出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你要怎麼補償我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反過來想吧  早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是晴天  很熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不換冬裝才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我都想把袖子捲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不如現在就捲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:01.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了早苗  還好今天很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你臉皮真厚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也好冷啊  可以把袖子放下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好  終於到午飯時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,帶便當了嗎  木村
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,他食物中毒請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是有新遊戲發售  逃課了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,櫻井  也感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,偶爾也一個人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.01,Takagi san—Picture 04-5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1486,784)}{\fad(400,400)}便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,偶爾一個人吃也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:20.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不僅有窗戶  風景不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,炸雞塊  是最棒的配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然還是有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:42.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為看西片你孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜你是不是會寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就來捉弄你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,覺得我會寂寞就來捉弄我  有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片的炸雞塊看起來挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要用它打賭  和我比賽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,出手了啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  要是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就把那個用蓮藕做的菜給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,藕夾是吧  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肉類配菜可是便當的生命線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我決不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼  你猜一下這個飯糰是什麼餡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很單純但又很難猜  不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能根據高木同學的配菜來推測嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行  好像很難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,蒙一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行  輸了炸雞塊就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,風險太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  來對答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:24.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  我可不會看漏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:28.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,旁邊的飯糰有一點鮭魚露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,藕夾歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正確答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,梅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我把炸雞塊拿走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說的也是  那麼精緻的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼能咬定兩個飯糰是同一種餡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的炸雞塊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看你這麼可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是用藕夾和你的炸雞塊交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:08.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:15.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼就換一個懲罰遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,換一個懲罰遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,懲罰遊戲…難道是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要餵我吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,玩什麼好呢  懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難道說  你想讓我餵你吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:01.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那可真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是比我一個人吃飯要有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那下次還一起吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:19.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次我遂了你的願  來餵你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都說了我才不想被你喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:36.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看啊  我昨天拍到了UFO的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:40.40,Takagi san—Picture 04-6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1532,370)}{\fad(1000,950)}UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好假啊  估計是蟲子什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨晚天空突然閃過一道閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我一回頭  就發現了UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我剛舉起鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,它一瞬間就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高尾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你還在相信UFO這種鬼話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,別用那種憐憫的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:05.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,區區日日野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,區區高尾  那是什麼語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:13.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對不起對不起對不起對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且那張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是你單手拋出什麼會發光的東西才拍到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還試了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你你你你在說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我跑步時都看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你倒是跟我打聲招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不要  怪噁心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看起來就是普通的石子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:53.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想拍出UFO一樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,午休的時候高尾他們在鬧騰的那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,UFO真浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:08.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要扔囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這怎麼看都只是石子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是扔得不夠快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總之再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:26.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,覺得UFO存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,當然存在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:40.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為你說得也太理所當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不說這個  繼續扔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不行嗎  要不試試小一點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學不相信有UFO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:04.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯…不相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總覺得很不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你真是不懂浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,浪漫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,請繼續扔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,總有點不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你真執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:35.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,話說  要浪漫的話還是拍真正的UFO更浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那要是有真的當然會拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我是外星人  也不會在西片面前現身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可不想引起騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過  出來捉弄一下人好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就把高木同學這樣不相信UFO的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全部抓起來然後嚇尿他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就算被西片抓走也無妨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:13.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,剛剛的應該扔歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拍到完美的UFO了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:25.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,厲害  跟真的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把這傳到網上一定會引起熱議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我會一炮走紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  那個也許是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:48.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  拍到巨像真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.82,Takagi san—Picture 04-7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,254)}豆之湯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.51,Takagi san—Picture 04-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.2\pos(1534,382)}{\fad(360,0)}幾小時前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誒  今天你要去公共澡堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  家裡的浴缸壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你大概幾點去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想  大概7點多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,…她這麼說  我還以為她會等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,該說有點失望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是說有點寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒被捉弄就偷著樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.90,Takagi san—Picture 04-9,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.522\pos(800,226)}商品請逐個購買
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.90,Takagi san—Picture 04-10,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.382\pos(290,516)}找零?退貨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對嘛  喝點水果牛奶靜下心來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誒  西片是水果派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就要咖啡牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你…你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:28.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒  還以為你沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,聽你這語氣  你有在找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:38.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也…沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我泡澡比較費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:46.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,於是估著西片出浴的時間提前進去泡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感覺好像輸了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學身上散發著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,香皂的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不覺得很新鮮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我們像這樣在夜晚一併走著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都不太能看清對方的臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  要不要來比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以啊  什麼比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:36.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,先害羞臉紅的人就算輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:37.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為天色太暗無法確認對方的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只有自己坦白才能決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好歹能拉扯到平局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以  不過不可以自己說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:51.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為自己又不能知道自己臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:05.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然很暗  但這個距離就能確認了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  你已經臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是我贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都還沒開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,被人靠這麼近怎麼可能不會臉紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:20.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也有可能是泡到臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.98,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我倒覺得已經過了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可以再確認一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全被她耍得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我就走這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,天色很暗  我送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:14.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這停頓是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說什麼奇怪的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:21.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這麼黑也看不清她是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那句話像是對戀人說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我家很近  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:37.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:46.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可能也泡得太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:47.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再見啦  晚上別著涼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還有西片  你臉很紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都說了是泡到臉紅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:04.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是  你根本沒在看我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.12,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}どうして君が泣くの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:16.97,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}まだ僕も泣いていないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}自分より  悲しむから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}つらいのがどっちか  わからなくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:38.39,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ガラクタだったはずの今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:45.81,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ふたりなら  宝物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.21,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}そばにいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:58.71,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君のために出来ることが  僕にあるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:10.30,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}いつも君に  ずっと君に  笑っていてほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.95,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ひまわりのような  まっすぐなその優しさを  温もりを全部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:29.29,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}これからは僕も 届けて行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ここにある幸せに 気づいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:11.12,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你為何會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:16.97,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}明明我還未落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:23.28,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是比我更悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:30.57,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}還是更加痛苦  我已搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:38.39,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本是破銅爛鐵的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:45.81,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}兩人一起的話  就將成為寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:49.21,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:58.71,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我能否為你做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:10.30,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}想讓你一直笑  想要你永遠笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:22.95,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今後我也想想將向日葵般  那直率的溫柔和溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:29.29,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}全部送到你心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:37.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因為察覺到了幸福就在此處
